0.jpeg 247w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-00.05.41-768x934.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-00.05.41-370x450.jpeg 370w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-00.05.41.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 842px) 100vw, 842px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c3bf5e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0c3bf5e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab36ed6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ab36ed6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fd47dac elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fd47dac\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Itinerary<\/h3>\n<p><b>Morning Pick-Up:<br><\/b>Your adventure begins with a pick-up from your riad or hotel in Marrakech. Enjoy a scenic drive through the Moroccan countryside, passing traditional villages and olive groves as you make your way to the Ouzoud Falls.<\/p>\n<p><b>Explore the Waterfalls:<br><\/b>Upon arrival, you\u2019ll be greeted by the breathtaking sight of the cascading waterfalls. Take a guided walk along the trails, which offer stunning viewpoints of the falls and the surrounding nature. You might even spot playful monkeys in the area!<\/p>\n<p><b>Boat Ride (Optional):<br><\/b>For a unique experience, take an optional boat ride to get up close to the waterfalls and feel the refreshing mist on your face.<\/p>\n<p><b>Lunch Break:<br><\/b>Enjoy a traditional Moroccan lunch at one of the local restaurants near the waterfalls, with picturesque views of the falls as your backdrop.<\/p>\n<p><b>Relax and Unwind:<br><\/b>After lunch, take some time to relax, explore the area, or dip your feet in the cool waters. The tranquil atmosphere is perfect for unwinding and enjoying the beauty of nature.<\/p>\n<p><b>Return to Marrakech:<br><\/b>In the late afternoon, your driver will take you back to Marrakech, ensuring a comfortable and relaxing journey.<\/p>\n<p><b>Highlights:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Visit the magnificent Ouzoud Waterfalls, Morocco\u2019s tallest cascades.<\/p>\n<p>Enjoy a scenic drive through traditional villages and olive groves.<\/p>\n<p>Take a guided walk with stunning views of the falls.<\/p>\n<p>Optional boat ride for a closer view of the waterfalls.<\/p>\n<p>Savor a delicious Moroccan lunch with a view of the cascades.<\/p>\n<p>This one-day trip to Ouzoud Waterfalls is perfect for nature lovers and those looking to experience the tranquil beauty of Morocco&#8217;s countryside. Join us for an unforgettable adventure!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>One-Day Trip to Ouzoud Waterfalls Escape the hustle and bustle of Marrakech and immerse yourself in nature with a one-day trip to the stunning Ouzoud Waterfalls. Known as one of Morocco&#8217;s most spectacular natural wonders, these 110-meter waterfalls are surrounded by lush greenery and offer a peaceful retreat. Itinerary Morning Pick-Up:Your adventure begins with a [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11313,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11689","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11689","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11689"}],"version-history":[{"count":26,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11689\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12791,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11689\/revisions\/12791"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11313"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11689"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}